metadata.title: ChronoStory Map and Monster Database
metadata.author: helloshorty
metadata.description: Complete map and monster database for ChronoStory (MapleStory Worlds)

notes: PM me in Discord (helloshorty) to request modifications or supplement missing information
Special thanks to @asteriskos for mapping out Maple Island
Map Links that are paired (e.g. A1 - A1) indicate bi-directional portals, while individual links refer to one-way portals
Map Links that start with M refer to portals that transition you to another town
Added images to find Hidden Streets more easily. PM me if you cannot find it
